name: GEL/LUBRICANT PERTO 3 OZ F/ FOOD PROC
CLEANER OVEN MR D RTU 1 GAL
description: Oven & Grill Cleaner RTU. Removes burned-on carbonized soil and grill residue. Ready-to-use formula, just spray on or brush on. Spray on surfaces under 200°F, allow to penetrate for 5 min, then wipe with a damp sponge. For heavy soil allow 10 min to penetrate.

name: CLEANER MR D COOK LINE RTU 32 OZ CLING
description: Cleaner/Degreaser. Cook line cleaner for ovens, griddles, fryers and rotisseries. Designed to penetrate baked-on carbonized soils on vertical surfaces. Do not apply on surfaces over 200°F. Dilution ratio: 4 oz to 1 gallon of water, allow 5 min to penetrate.

name: CLEANER FRYER MR D PACKETS 8 OZ
description: Fryer Cleaner. Powerful alkaline powder contains sodium hydroxide for fast, efficient carbon removal. Eliminates caked-on carbon and emulsifies grease for fresh-tasting fried foods. Dilution: One portion pack per every wash. Boil 20 to 30 minutes, then drain and brush side with stiff brush, flush with water when finished.

name: DETERGENT TABS ACTIVE GREEN ICOMBI OVEN

CLEANER FOR COMBI 90 TABS PER BUCKET
CLEANER OVEN & GRILL 32 OZ NON CAUSTIC
POWDER FRYER OIL MIRACLE FILTER 40 LBS
description: Powder. Removes minute carbon particles that host bacteria that attack oil and create acidity--increases the life of oil and improves quality of food. Magnesium sulfate powder also removes free fatty acids and oxidized acids which are major contributors to oil degradation.

name: CLEANER MR D OVEN & GRILL AERO
description: Oven Cleaner. Spray on-clean off. Works in minutes on caked food, grease and other foods. Spray on surfaces under 200°F, allow to penetrate for 5 min, then wipe with a damp sponge. For use on porcelain, glass, ceramics, stainless steel and cast iron surfaces.

name: CLEANER OVEN/GRILL BREAK-UP 19OZ AEROSOL
